Paper: hep-th/9401138

Date: 1994-01-27

Title: A New Class of Supersymmetric Theories

Authors: Ashok Das

Comments: 9 pages

We construct a class of quantum mechanical theories which are invariant underfermionic transformations similar to supersymmetry transformations. Thegenerators of the transformations in this case, however, satisfy a BRST-likealgebra.